com.mousebird.maply

Class ImageLoaderReturn

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.LoaderReturn
      • com.mousebird.maply.ImageLoaderReturn

  • public class ImageLoaderReturn
extends LoaderReturn
    This version of the loader return is used by the ImageLoaderInterpreter. When image tiles load, the interpeter fills in these contents, which can include any sort of ComponentObject and, of course, images.
